                "caption": "Figure 3:Query-variation analysis under two backbone–model pairings. In each row, the left panel shows consistency among the generated responses in a shared embedding space, while the right panel shows consistency of the corresponding response representations across layers. The first row compares the relatively low-unification pair OmniGen2 and Qwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct; the second row compares the more aggressively unified Show-o2 and its Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct reference. Read row-wise, the figure asks how strongly unification training has altered the inherited backbone behavior.",
